The '''''Droo''''' was a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] in service to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. It was assigned to the [[Airam sector/Legends|Airam sector]].

When the decision was made to construct a Rebel [[Shipyard/Legends|shipyard]] in Airam [[Realspace/Legends|space]], the ''Droo'' was assigned to the convoy which would bring the needed supplies and personnel. The ''Droo'' was transporting troops to be used as station security and orbital defense. Unfortunately for the Alliance, the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] learned of the planned Rebel shipyard, and it ambushed the construction convoy in the [[Rocrin system/Legends|Rocrin system]]. The ''Droo'' was destroyed in the ambush along with the rest of the convoy.

